WEBVTT

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:30.520
Are these not important?

00:00:32.159 --> 00:00:33.616
I would argue

00:00:33.640 --> 00:00:37.320
that the most important
infrastructure we have are minds,

00:00:38.360 --> 00:00:39.640
educated minds.

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:47.496
President Bourguiba helped establish
free, high-quality education

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:49.840
for every boy and every girl.

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:54.816
And together with millions
of other Tunisians,

00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:57.360
I'm deeply indebted
to that historic decision.

00:00:58.040 --> 00:01:00.160
And that's what brought me here today,